            <h2>New Meditation Centre</h2>
            <p>
              Our goal is to acquire a new facility that meets zoning requirements for holding religious assemblies, in order to resume our mindfulness and meditation programs, Dhamma discussions, childrenâ€™s programs, stress relief programs, counselling, retreats and daily sermons.
              <!--
