              We estimate a new facility would require a minimum investment of 1.5 million dollars. The current property is valued at approximately $500,000 plus we would be able to obtain a bank loan for another $300,000. However, this leaves a shortfall of $700,000 which means we will need to raise this amount.
              <!--
              It takes about a minimum investment of 1.5 million dollars to acquire a new facility with proper bylaw permissions. At the moment, we can get about $500,000 for this by selling the current property of the centre and another $300,000 as a bank loan. The remaining $700,000 needs to be raised.
              -->
            </p>
            <!--<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#section2" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p> -->
